formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
As per section 13 (1) of the RERA Act 2016, A promoter shall not accept more than 10 % of the value of consideration without first entering into written agreement with Allottees,  in few cases company has accepted more than 10 % of the consideration without entering into the written agreement (as per annexure A). 
As per Written representation received by management that despite company sending the model agreement for signatures and execution of Allottees, the Allottees never reverted with the signed agreements and continued to pay the money as per contractual milestones as per RERA. The company has also received the building use permission wide Ahmedabad Urban Development Authority (AUDA) CMP/5352/6/2017/425 dated 26th July 2017 and hence the final sale deed will now be executed with all such Allottees further project is registered as ongoing project under RERA
